            <string language="en">Chapter about data protection, computer crime, the impact of ICT, part of e-materials for computer science and informatics. Chapter contents: personal data, passwords, intrusion, viruses / worms, firewall.</string>

virus/vers, mur à l'épreuve du feu.</string>

refrattaria.</string>

datos personales, palabras de paso, intrusión, virus/gusanos,
